After crisis hits and families battle wildlife, bad water, failing power, and isolation, the Raneys bring experience and grit to pull each homestead back from the brink and restore reliable access to clean water.
Stream Homestead Rescue on Discovery+ ► https://www.discoveryplus.com/show/homestead-rescue

Marty, Matt and Misty Raney use their building, farming and hunting expertise to help people who strive to live off the grid.

author: Discovery
description:
Bear Grylls brings us to some of the coldest places on earth, from barren fields of Siberia to a glacier in Iceland, demonstrating how to survive through freezing winds, dangerous avalanches, icy waters, and plunging temperatures.
Stream Full Episodes of Man vs. Wild: https://www.discoveryplus.com/show/man-vs-wild

#Discovery #ManVsWild 

About Man vs. Wild:
Bear Grylls has served with the British Special forces, climbed Everest and explored the Arctic. He shares how to survive the toughest and most remote environments by putting himself in the position of a stranded tourist.
